text: Saurabh Singh may refer to: *Saurabh Singh (cricketer) (born 1997), Indian cricketer *Saurabh Singh (Chhattisgarh politician) (born 1974), Indian politician, Member of Legislative Assembly for Akaltara *Saurabh Singh (politician), Indian politician, Member of 17th Legislative Assembly, Uttar Pradesh
